---
// Sveltia CMS admin page — served at /blog/admin/.
//
// Sveltia loads its config from ./config.yml (same directory). That file lives
// in public/admin/config.yml so Astro serves it as a static asset alongside
// this rendered page.
//
// Edit public/admin/config.yml to point Sveltia at your site's GitHub repo.
// See INTEGRATION.md → "Enable the CMS" for OAuth setup.
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />
    <title>Content Manager</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="data:," />
  </head>
  <body>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@sveltia/cms/dist/sveltia-cms.js" is:inline></script>
  </body>
</html>
